Altay, Croft, + Pelupessy, 2008
SPHRAY: A Smoothed Particle Hydrodynamics Ray Tracer for Radiative Transfer - Monte Carlo RT scheme that integrates SPH kernel to get radiation fields (rather than interpolating particles to grid). Calculates non-equilibrium ionization and temperature. Uses tests from Iliev et al. " quick Axis Aligned Bounding Box (AABB) test taken from computer graphics applications allows for the acceleration of the raytracing component."
